<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Register</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen"
  >
    <div class="container bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Register</h1>

      <div class="mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-red-600">
          Bad Practice: Weak Password Allowed
        </h2>
        <form action="/register-bad" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
          <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>" />
          <div>
            <label
              for="username-bad"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
              >Username:</label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              id="username-bad"
              name="username"
              class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="email-bad"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
              >Email:</label
            >
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email-bad"
              name="email"
              class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="password-bad"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
              >Password (e.g., "123"):</label
            >
            <input
              type="password"
              id="password-bad"
              name="password"
              class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full py-2 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-red-500"
          >
            Register (Bad)
          </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          ลองใช้รหัสผ่านง่ายๆ เช่น "123" หรือ "password"
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-green-600">
          Best Practice: Strong Password Required
        </h2>
        <form action="/register-best" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
          <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>" />
          <div>
            <label
              for="username-best"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
              >Username:</label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              id="username-best"
              name="username"
              class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="email-best"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
              >Email:</label
            >
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email-best"
              name="email"
              class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="password-best"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
              >Password (Min 8 chars, incl. uppercase, lowercase, number,
              special char):</label
            >
            <input
              type="password"
              id="password-best"
              name="password"
              class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-green-500 focus:border-green-500"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full py-2 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-green-500"
          >
            Register (Best)
          </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          ลองใช้รหัสผ่านที่ไม่ตรงตามเงื่อนไขเพื่อดูข้อผิดพลาด
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-center text-gray-600">
        มีบัญชีอยู่แล้ว?
        <a href="/login" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
          >เข้าสู่ระบบที่นี่</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
